            "releaseNotes": "Dive into our brand-new slideshow modes \u2014 choose your favorite style and speed for the perfect playback!\nLove looping? Now you can play your videos and GIFs on repeat as many times as you like in slideshow mode.\nNotes are safer than ever \u2014 we fixed a bug that sometimes prevented them from saving properly.\nPhoto imports now land exactly where they should \u2014 no more surprises!\nFixed a bug with App oppening tracker.\nThanks for being part of our journey \u2014 enjoy the smoother, smarter experience!",
            "version": "2.19",
            "wrapperType": "software",
